# ✅ VERIFICATION CHECKLIST
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# After setting .env files, verify:
#
# □ Backend can connect to MongoDB
# □ Frontend builds without errors (npm run build)
# □ Admin panel builds without errors (npm run build)
# □ Backend API is accessible at VITE_API_BASE_URL
# □ WebSocket connects at VITE_SOCKET_URL
# □ Email sending works (check RESEND_API_KEY)
# □ Google OAuth works (check GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID)
# □ Images load correctly (CORS configured)
# □ Maintenance mode button visible for super admin
# □ All services running without errors
#


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 📞 SUPPORT & TROUBLESHOOTING
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Common Issues:
#
# Q: Frontend can't connect to backend?
# A: Check VITE_API_BASE_URL is correct and backend is running
#
# Q: Images not loading?
# A: Check CORS is configured, backend FRONTEND_URL matches actual domain
#
# Q: WebSocket not connecting?
# A: Check VITE_SOCKET_URL is correct and uses https:// for production
#
# Q: Build fails with "env variable not found"?
# A: Make sure .env file is in the project root directory
#
# Q: Maintenance button not showing?
# A: Verify admin is logged as super admin (isSuperAdmin=true in DB)
#
# Q: Payment info not showing?
# A: Check VITE_PLATFORM_BANK_* variables are set correctly
#

